### List all payments
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/payments
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Record a payment against a bill (ROLE_FINANCE)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/payments
Authorization: Bearer {{financeToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

